{
  "3184640": {
    "name": "复生之泪：泛山行",
    "steam_appid": 3184640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/9de5731093e50ae4ba14784cf9d5162e.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的人生将在巍峨险峻的山前开始……这是一款最多支持4人合作的地牢探索角色扮演游戏，你将与众多角色一同攀登并探索泛山。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/570ccb14e3f4762bc5d420c17b62de2f.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要探索并攀登随机生成的山峰，寻找并击败强大的Boss，努力让你的冒险之旅走得更高、更远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/e84ee4b71e87d6ff953ad5683d3a9b48.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中，你将获得强大的新技能、武器和装备，这些都是你生存下去的必备之物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/b2256537e8fd48106f2fd9ea453d6b74.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/b85b5b9a56d201452b8745b08b369983.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以与最多4名玩家组队冒险！当然，如果你更喜欢独自挑战，也无需担心——你还可以邀请营地中的其他成员成为你的伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/d06c724441f879ab85fe6dfcbcfcd756.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的营地为每一次冒险做好准备。起初，只有你和你的思绪……但随着探索的深入，你会遇见很多愿意帮助你的人——从拥有独特技能的探险家，到可以在幕后提供帮助的专家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/40241a0136463eae5121fe8404afe9a6.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184640/extras/20ac5b0f7e5b15243726945712644131.avif?t=1771869000\" width=600 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的冒险旅程中，你会遇到许多形形色色的人物，并逐渐了解他们以及他们的动机。但你也可能被卷入一场百年战争的余波之中……</p>",
